All roads lead to the much anticipated Global Citizen Festival: Mandela 100 taking place at the FNB Stadium this afternoon. Despite numerous warnings and even incentives given to fans in a bid to get them through the gates early, the last minute rush to get inside the stadium is underway. Fans were promised the chance for a free ticket upgrade, among other things in order to avoid long queues, however not even that could do the trick. There was also a delay in letting the fans who were on time into the stadium.  